  "title": "SOCIAL WORKER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position Overview:</strong><br />We are seeking dedicated Social Workers to provide high-quality support and interventions for individuals and families across our service locations. You will play a key role in empowering communities, advocating for clients, and contributing to the development of best practices and policies.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver casework, counselling, and intervention planning to meet client needs</li><li>Advocate for families in collaboration with partner agencies and stakeholders</li><li>Plan and facilitate group programmes to strengthen community engagement</li><li>Contribute to policy development, service improvement initiatives, and professional practice standards</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Degree or Graduate Diploma in Social Work (For SASW Registration) </strong></li><li>Strong collaboration, networking, and problem-solving skills</li><li>Adaptable, tech-savvy, and committed to social justice principles</li><li>Ability to work independently while contributing to a multidisciplinary team</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive salary and clear career progression pathways</li><li>Comprehensive training, mentorship, and professional supervision</li><li>Supportive work environment with flexible arrangements</li></ul><p><strong>Application:</strong><br />Interested candidates are invited to submit their applications. Only shortlisted applicants will be contacted.<br /><br />Kindly email your resume in a detailed <strong>Word format</strong> to: <a href=\"mailto:enoch.cheong@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>enoch.cheong@peopleprofilers.com</em></a></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>People Profilers Pte Ltd</strong></p><p><strong>Address:</strong> 20 Cecil Street, #08-09, Plus Building, Singapore 049705</p><p><strong>Contact: </strong><a href=\"tel:+65 6950 9740\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">+65 6950 9740</a></p><p><strong>EA Licence No.:</strong> 02C4944</p><p><strong>EA Personnel Reg. No.: </strong>R21100787</p><p><strong>EA Personnel: </strong>Enoch Cheong</p>",
